---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - Lewisham Your Party">
    <main class="min-h-screen bg-yp-cream text-yp-slate p-8 md:p-16">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl border-t-8 border-yp-red mb-20">
            
            <a href="/" class="inline-block mb-8 text-yp-red font-bold uppercase tracking-wider hover:underline">
                &larr; Back to Home
            </a>
            
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading uppercase tracking-tighter mb-6">Terms of Service</h1>
            
            <div class="space-y-6 text-lg opacity-90">
                <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> 13 March 2026</p>

                <p>Welcome to the Lewisham Your Party website. By using this website, you agree to the following simple terms.</p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mt-8">1. About This Site</h2>
                <p>This website is built and maintained by local volunteers campaigning for Your Party in Lewisham. While we strive to keep all information regarding events, news, and campaigns accurate and up-to-date, the site is provided on an "as-is" basis.</p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mt-8">2. Acceptable Use</h2>
                <p>We built this site to organize local action. By using our website and contact forms, you agree not to:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>Use the site for any unlawful purpose.</li>
                    <li>Spam our contact forms or attempt to overwhelm our systems.</li>
                    <li>Attempt to hack, scrape, or otherwise compromise the security of the website.</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mt-8">3. Intellectual Property</h2>
                <p>The "Your Party" name, logos, and branding are the property of Your Party UK Ltd. Local content, articles, and photographs are generated by our volunteer team. You are welcome to share our news updates and event links to help spread the word, but please do not impersonate our local branch.</p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mt-8">4. Third-Party Links</h2>
                <p>Our site may contain links to the national Your Party website or other external resources. We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices of these external sites.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>